{"tid":759764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登已經劣質到連轉載新聞都不可信","createTime":"2018-07-29T02:47:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T04:53:26.000Z","uid":57844,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c347bb1f31cd35abf1e8b0807d5e868a9f1b716a","tid":759764,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"成班小學雞改新聞"},{"pid":"8163f3473744f9141c7c4d945dc85dd7ce47757f","tid":759764,"uid":105995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T02:48:15.000Z","msg":"child登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31682af2a6573067749402a587059544981660e","tid":759764,"uid":191338,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:51:26.000Z","msg":"一帶一路：差佬掃黃，拘捕多名外籍雞。當中24人有愛滋<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/bswsQS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/bswsQS</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180130/mobile/bkn-20180130011152311-0130_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180130011152311-0130_00822_001.html&d=EiDfJdQdG%2FZi7HAVwIfDtDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=431bd7b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180130/mobile/bkn-20180130011152311-0130_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180727/mobile/bkn-20180727180710397-0727_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180727%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180727180710397-0727_00822_001.html&d=EiDfJdQdG%2FZi7HAVwIfDtDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0a5a7d54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180727/mobile/bkn-20180727180710397-0727_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n2003年4月1日：14歲改《明報》網頁，訛稱「香港成為疫埠」，警方隨即追查消息來源，並拘捕涉事14歲男生。最後裁判官判被告12個月社署監管令。8<br />\n<br />\n2006年8月26日：請教網友製炸彈炸「迪迪尼」，警方事後將男子拘捕，他最終承認浪費警力罪，被判罰120小時社會服務令及罰款10,000元。<br />\n<br />\n2008年9月22日：34歲無業青年及18歲文員在討論區謠傳東亞銀行將會倒閉，令銀行出現恐慌性擠提。裁判官判兩名被告簽保 5000 元並守行為兩年。<br />\n<br />\n2010年4月1日：18歲男生留言指愚人節在時代廣場放置炸彈，青年隨後被控以向他人傳達有炸彈的虛假消息罪，裁判官判被告自簽保5,000元及守行為一年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/114558_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F114558_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ea72df5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/114600_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F114600_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4672c5cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/114603_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F114603_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a53b726d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/114757_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F114757_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=bcd85705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過其實比起19世紀已經輕好多自由好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://borderless-hk.com/2017/08/05/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%AB%A5%E5%B7%A5%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%A4%BF%E8%AC%A0%E8%A8%80/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fborderless-hk.com%2F2017%2F08%2F05%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25A4%25BF%25E8%25AC%25A0%25E8%25A8%2580%2F&d=EiDfJdQdG%2FZi7HAVwIfDtDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=69838ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://border